OL,3,COfcom ad rules and ITV regional/
OL,4,Cnational news requirements
OL,6,GIf you were watching ITV 1's quiz
OL,7,Gshow The 1% Club last night, you may
OL,8,Ghave faced a little puzzle of another
OL,9,Gsort.
OL,11,FThe show's "commercial" breaks were
OL,12,Fall packed with trailers.
OL,14,FOf course, most Pres enthusiasts and
OL,15,Fregular readers of this website know
OL,16,Fexactly why this was.
