OL,3,COfcom ad rules and ITV regional/
OL,4,Cnational news requirements
OL,6,FITV 1, Channel 4 and Channel 5 can
OL,7,Fonly run 40 minutes of ads between
OL,8,F6pm and 11pm but can run up to 12
OL,9,Fminutes in any one hour. This mean
OL,10,Fleaving some hours light or empty so
OL,11,Fmore ads can be packed around the
OL,12,Fmost popular or lucrative shows.
OL,14,FDuring the week it can at least be
OL,15,Fargued that there is a benefit to
OL,16,Fviewers ` it means fewer ads during
OL,17,Fthe news. This is one reason why
OL,18,FOfcom recently surprised many when it
OL,19,Fkicked plans to allow the PSBs to run
OL,20,Fas many ads as the other commercial
OL,21,Fchannels into the long grass.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/8
