OL,3,COfcom ad rules and ITV regional/
OL,4,Cnational news requirements
OL,6,FOfcom now intends to look at the
OL,7,Fissue holistically ` also taking into
OL,8,Faccount issues such as the renewal of
OL,9,Fthe licences for ITV and Channel 5
OL,10,Fand the Media Bill which is set to
OL,11,Fbecome law before the General
OL,12,FElection.
OL,14,FThere has been no public discussion
OL,15,Fas far as I am aware over whether
OL,16,Fthere should be changes to ITV 1's
OL,17,Fspecific public service obligations
OL,18,Fin the new licence period which
OL,19,Fstarts in January 2025.
