OL,3,COfcom ad rules and ITV regional/
OL,4,Cnational news requirements
OL,6,FThe discussions with Ofcom are likely
OL,7,Fto focus on what level of regional
OL,8,Fnews provision and dedicated output
OL,9,Fin the nations is sustainable.
OL,11,FBut there could be more to discuss to
OL,12,Fallow clarity going forward.
OL,14,FIt would be no bad thing if the new
OL,15,Flicences clearly set out the absolute
OL,16,Fminimum number of minutes of actual
OL,17,Flocal and national news which are
OL,18,Frequired.
