OL,3,COfcom ad rules and ITV regional/
OL,4,Cnational news requirements
OL,6,FAs I understand it, the current
OL,7,Fobligations slightly conflate the
OL,8,Factual length of the programme with
OL,9,Fthe slot duration.
OL,11,FITV 1 has to run 30 minutes of news
OL,12,Fin peak ` but does that mean a half
OL,13,Fhour billed programme including ads
OL,14,For an absolute minimum of 30 minutes
OL,15,Fof actual news?
OL,17,FIf the rules clearly indicated how
OL,18,Fmany minutes of actual news
OL,19,Fprogramming had to be broadcast, then
OL,20,Fthere would be no question of cutting
OL,21,Fthe news simply because of additional
OL,22,Fadvertising.
