OL,6,FThe minimum duration of news
OL,7,Fbulletins can and should be clearly
OL,8,Fset. Let's say a half hour news
OL,9,Fprogramme actually means 23 minutes.
OL,11,FBut at best maintaining the current
OL,12,Frules much longer means more "trailer
OL,13,Fbreaks" at the weekend.
OL,15,FAt worst they add to the difficulties
OL,16,Ffacing ITV and Channel 4.
